mbiont trees. Its rooting in the\ntool Coala allows it to estimate the probabilities of the events even in the\ncase of large datasets. We evaluate our method on synthetic and real datasets.\nThe software is available at\nhttps://sites.google.com/view/blerinasinaimeri/software/amocoala\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Mon, 23 May 2022 07:01:17 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Thu, 13 Oct 2022 08:09:11 GMT"}],"update_date":"2022-10-14"}
